sentences: Trishna Gurung (Nepali: तृष्णा गुरुङ, born 28 September 1985) is a Nepali singer and also a coach of The Voice of Nepal Season 3, a reality show.
She sang popular numbers including the title song of Maya Pirati, Khani ho yahmu, Gaine Dajaile , Khani ho yamu etc. songs.
Trishna Gurung is a young Composer, Singer and Lyricist of Nepal Music Industry.
Her most popular song is Maya Pirati uploaded on YouTube.
She started her music career in 2007 and her first song Daiba Janos in 2007.
